NPM. 
Enter `npm help` to get general help.

# Updating NPM.
`npm install npm -g`

# Installing a module.
npm install <module name>

#Listing all the module dependencies.
`npm ls`

# Installing and saving the dependencies  in a package.json file.

`npm install --save`

# Writing npm test.

'touch test.js'
edit package.json to point to test.js.

